        I'm a noob but i would make: <br> <br>1. [new layer] -circle u need <- color= white ? DON'T LOOSE UR SELECTION YET :P <br>2. [new layer] make the circle again in another color :D fx. purple <br>3. gaussian blur your purple circle till ur satisfied <br>4. take the white circle ontop of the purple layr and toy with the rest <br> <br>- REALLY I <b>Could be wrong </b>
