        -- Posted by Raptor on 10:47 am on Dec. 13, 2001<p>
        i didn't use black. its a really really really really dark purple.. so dark that it looks black. if you want, start with a normal purple. then go through the steps, then adjust the hue/saturation on the purple layer until its a dark color, but you still have the glow.

